essage from our ceo free consultation  cost of care take the guesswork out of long term care planning start here   genworth to be acquired by china oceanwide learn more from genworths ceo and president tom mcinerney read his message   with planningcomes confidence having a plan for how you’ll handle long term care can make all the difference request a free consultation   customer service access your account and forms online claims start your online claim process pay online make a payment  no login required why consider long term care insurance having a plan for long term care can help you find practical and affordable ways to help pay the high costs of long term care services ready to learn more about long term care planning long term care insurance   concerned about paying for care you can create a personal income plan to help cover any purpose  living expenses medical expenses and the cost of long term care whether receiving care at home in an assisted living community or another type of facility immediate need annuity   youll be glad you picked mortgage insurance mortgage insurance mi makes it possible for homebuyers to get a house with less than  down payment and with a low down payment buyers can get into a home years sooner mortgage insurance     products long term care insurance immediate need annuity mortgage insurance genworth global links about us investors newsroom careers site tools site map privacy terms of use fraud  information protection social media   our financial products are offeredunderwritten by one or more of the following genworth life and annuity insurance company genworth life insurance company genworth life insurance company of new york only genworth life insurance company of new york is admitted in and conducts business in new york genworth mortgage insurance corporation genworth financial mortgage insurance pty limited genworth financial mortgage insurance limited genworth residential mortgage insurance corporation of nc genworth financi